{"id": 1780, "genre": 1000, "title": "你是哪种类型的互联网学习者？", "description": "在0和1的世界里，你都是怎么给自己充电的？还有哪些超值的办法，请在留言区跟全人类共享。（题图来自：Vimeo）", "record_count": 9119, "comment_count": 41, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170703202308wlyLr8jE79qVoeHA.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-03T17:00:03Z", "questions": [{"id": 2551, "title": "你是哪种类型的互联网学习者？", "content": "你是哪种类型的互联网学习者？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 218728, "content": "公开课终身学生，入了好几个门了", "image": "img/option/option/20170703202433ClborunaIdUcNSYA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218729, "content": "纪录片学习者，系统又愉快地学东西", "image": "img/option/option/20170703202514xa0sryA8qQ9OdiJK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218735, "content": "播客学习者，下载了很多杂项音频，解放眼睛，随时能听", "image": "img/option/option/20170703202824mRrTjI0Bd3xycNsW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218731, "content": "TED型学习者，听君一席话胜读十年书，比较迅速", "image": "img/option/option/20170703202616v76FdYRKUD9kSlrA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218732, "content": "新闻来龙去脉学习者，靠看详细新闻搞清楚大公司、恐怖组织怎么回事", "image": "img/option/option/20170703202647pi1zMDrq56uLSvoU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218733, "content": "问答论坛学习者，针对性强的问答网站上能学到很多东西", "image": "img/option/option/20170703202724mJvV1c23GbNY7gCR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218734, "content": "购物学者，买东西看测评帖和技术分析获得新知", "image": "img/option/option/20170703202753TSGdrw83gBxmZVp0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218741, "content": "垂直论坛学者，NBA到汽车，护肤到占星，吹水加学习", "image": "img/option/option/20170703204838xkeKwPGSCrnJI76F.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218730, "content": "方法论研究者，会试各种提升效率，提升学习质量的方法", "image": "img/option/option/20170703202554TfBAXR6dlnU2mgwr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}